<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="144" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,1597]" pageId="2" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,268,151,175]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="144" reason="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Reddish yellow with black markings on mesoscutum and metasomal tergites; occipital carina entirely absent; mesosternum with posterior transverse carina complete; fore wing vein 1cu-a distad of M&amp;RS.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
